! --- PASO 4: Asignar Puertos a PCs (Ejemplos) ---

! Puerto para una PC de Ventas

interface f0/10

 switchport mode access

 switchport access vlan 65

 spanning-tree portfast

 no shutdown

 exit



! Puerto para una PC de TI

interface f0/11

 switchport mode access

 switchport access vlan 66

 spanning-tree portfast

 no shutdown

 exit



